<h2 id="selected-research-projects">Selected Research Projects</h2>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">2022 -- 2024</code>
<em><a href="https://www.gu.se/forskning/framtidaarbetsliv">Arbetsliv under covid-19-pandemin</a></em></p>

<p>Asks what we can learn from the experiences from remote and hybrid work during covid-19 to make worklife more inclusive for people with disabilities.</p>

